Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Disneyland
Description: A world famous amusement park for all ages with immersive rides, first rate performances and shows, and high quality food located in southern California.

Name: Central Park
Description: An often busy but quaint park located in Downtown Davis, CA that has a large playground and carousel, a flower garden, open green space for communal gatherings or activities, and extra space that holds the weekly famer's market.

Name: Waterfront Park
Description: A bustling park in Louisville, KY with three playgrounds, a splash pad, swinging benches overlooking the Ohio river, and the entrance to a pedestrian/cyclist bridge connecting Kentucky to Indianna.

Name: International Rose Test Garden
Description: A vibrant and peaceful rose garden located in Washington Park in Portland, Oregon.

Name: The Outer Banks
Description: A string of peninsulas and small islands off the coast of North Carolina that have lighthouses, wild roaming horses, beautiful beaches, and diverse plant life.
